and Paul has to address that

00:25:08.522 --> 00:25:08.808
issue.
 

00:25:08.808 --> 00:25:12.902
Any other issues of sexuality
that Paul has to address in 1

00:25:12.902 --> 00:25:13.890
Corinthians?
 

00:25:13.890 --> 00:25:15.210
There's one more major one.
 

00:25:15.210 --> 00:25:16.940
Student: 
&gt;

00:25:16.940 --> 00:25:18.259
Prof: Pardon?
 

00:25:18.259 --> 00:25:19.298
Student: 
&gt;

00:25:19.298 --> 00:25:20.211
Prof: Virginity.
 

00:25:20.211 --> 00:25:22.594
He does bring it up but that's
not as big an issue for him as

00:25:22.594 --> 00:25:24.380
