00:25:24.380 --> 00:25:27.500
Remember in 1 Corinthians 7:1
they seem to have asked him,

00:25:27.500 --> 00:25:31.394
this is actually put into
quotation marks in some of your

00:25:31.394 --> 00:25:34.595
